# Documentation sync

When changing API behavior, registration/update flows, status transitions, auth, pooling, or stack details:

1. Update **README.md** (API examples, architecture, config tables).
2. Update **docs/demo.html** (sections 1–4: purpose, flows, status diagram, technology).

Both files must describe the same behavior. If one changes, update the other in the same change set.

Demo page path: `docs/demo.html` (open locally in a browser for presentations).
